    <item>
      <title>中国的财政刺激计划可能比表面上看起来更大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/does-china-s-fiscal-stimulus-plan-square-with-gdp-growth-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国领导层看似克制的2024年预算计划令投资者失望。但除了标题数据之外，仔细观察就会发现，该计划的影响力可能比最初想象的更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/does-china-s-fiscal-stimulus-plan-square-with-gdp-growth-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本顶级债券经理预计今年销售又将强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/top-japanese-bond-managers-see-another-strong-year-for-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本顶级债务承销商预计，无论央行在政策上采取什么行动，公司债券和武士债券销售在 4 月份开始的财年中将再次表现强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/top-japanese-bond-managers-see-another-strong-year-for-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能竞争担忧导致预测疲软，Adobe 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/adobe-projects-lackluster-sales-with-ai-competition-intensifying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adobe Inc. 在发布本季度销售前景疲弱后，在盘后交易中下跌约 10%，引发了人们对新的专注于人工智能的初创公司构成竞争威胁的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/adobe-projects-lackluster-sales-with-ai-competition-intensifying</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
